worksheets.name: Spending on Edu vs Terciarty Scatter

tasks.name: Assert SQL
tasks.sql:
SELECT
  country "Country",
  region "Region",
  CAST(
    SUM(
      patent_applications_resident + patent_applications_nonresident + trademark_applications_total
    ) AS CHAR
  ) "Patent and Trade Mark Applications, total"
FROM
  worldbank_development_indicators
GROUP BY
  country,
  region
HAVING
  AVG(government_expenditure_on_education_pc_of_GDP) > 4
  AND AVG(gross_enrollment_ratio_terciary_both_sexes) > 50
